Katepart-syntax-twig provides Twig syntax highlighting for Katepart. It is released under the new BSD license.

This project is not affiliated with Twig, Kate or Katepart.

Usage example
*************
1. Copy twig.xml to ~/home/.kde4/share/apps/katepart/syntax/twig.xml
2. (Re)start Kate or whatever editor you are using


Author
